                                <h4><strong>E-Attendance</strong></h4>                          
                                
                                <figure class="thumb col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                                <img class="img-responsive" src="news/images/2018/e-Attendance-05Mar2018-02.jpg" alt="" >		
                                </figure> 
								
								<p>
								<br>
								E-Attendance and content sharing system of St. Xavier's College, Kolkata was formally inaugurated by Rev Fr. Dr. Dominic Savio, SJ in the presence of Vice Principals, Rev. Fr. Dr. S Xavier, SJ and Rev Fr. Peter A, SJ on 5th March, 2018 at 11 am. 
								This will help the college in recording and maintaining attendance of students and sharing content, notes and circulars in a paper less environment. 
								In future college are going to process e-admit card.
								</p>  
																		
								</div><!--//item-->

                                <div class="item">
                               
                                <h4><strong>Visit by team from SUNY (Oswego)</strong></h4>                          
                                
                                <figure class="thumb col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                                <img class="img-responsive" src="news/images/2018/SUNY-Oswego-TeamVisit-Jan2018-03.jpg" alt="" >		
                                </figure> 
								
								<p>
								Visit by team from SUNY (Oswego) from 9-16th January,2018. <br>
								Team comprising of 9 students & 2 faculty members primarily attending education & service learning programmes, with the Dept of Education, St. Xavier's College.
								The programme began with an inauguration ceremony presided over by our Rector & Principal, Rev.Dr. Dominic Savio,S.J, Dr Panchali Sen & Dr Charlotte Simpson Veigas,at 9.15 am today.
								</p>  
																		
								</div><!--//item-->


                                <div class="item">
                               
                                <h4><strong>Annual Seminar of the Department of Computer Science</strong></h4>                          
                                
                                <figure class="thumb col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-4">
                                <img class="img-responsive" src="news/images/2017/FacultyImprovementProgramme-02-21Dec2017.jpg" alt="" >		
                                </figure> 
								
								<p>
								The Annual Seminar of the Department of Computer Science titled <b>"Enterprise Digitisation and Cyber Security"</b> was held on <b>21/12/2017</b> and the resource person was Dr. Dave Chatterjee. 
								This year the seminar was organised in association with the Department of Information Technology, the Academic Council and the IQAC of the College. 
								Dr. Chatterjee is a tenured Associate Professor, in the MIS department, at the Terry College of Business, The University of Georgia (UGA). Being an accomplished scholar, technology thought leader and an excellent orator, he effortlessly guided the audience through the nuances of Enterprise Digitisation and Cyber Security. 
								He explained the importance of digital security in an organisation and the execution of the same depends upon the alacrity of the employees of all levels of an organisation. 
								The seminar was extremely engaging and interactive and was attended by 30 faculty members of various departments of the College. 
								</p> 
																		
								</div><!--//item-->


