                                            <h4><strong>St. Xavier's upgraded to CE status</strong></h4>                                            
                                            <p>The UGC has upgraded St. Xavier's 
                                            College, Kolkata to the status of 
                                            &quot;College of Excellence (CE)&quot; w.e.f. 
                                            <b>1st April 2014 to 31st March 2019</b>. 
                                            <br>
                                            The UGC has also approved the 
                                            College's budget for Rs. Two Crores 
                                            for a period of five years for 
                                            college's upgradation.<br>
                                            St. Xavier's was a College with 
                                            Potential for Excellence (CPE) since 
                                            2006. It was also awarded the 
                                            autonomous status in 2006.<br>
